: "2", "bbox": [890.0, 741.8, 899.4, 760.5]}, {"text": "(23)", "bbox": [1003.7, 741.8, 1035.0, 760.5]}, {"text": "Derivatives not designated as hedging instruments:", "bbox": [153.2, 764.5, 561.3, 783.2]}, {"text": "Foreign currency forward contracts . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [190.7, 787.6, 547.0, 806.4]}, {"text": "Other income (expense), net", "bbox": [563.7, 787.6, 776.3, 806.4]}, {"text": "4", "bbox": [890.0, 787.6, 899.4, 806.4]}, {"text": "(4)", "bbox": [1013.1, 787.6, 1035.0, 806.4]}, {"text": "*", "bbox": [153.2, 827.7, 163.6, 848.6]}, {"text": "Amounts are insignificant (less than $1).", "bbox": [194.9, 827.7, 534.9, 848.6]}, {"text": "(1)", "bbox": [153.2, 852.7, 177.5, 873.6]}, {"text": "Represents the ineffective portion of the fixed price diesel swaps.", "bbox": [194.9, 852.7, 741.4, 873.6]}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [153.2, 877.7, 177.5, 898.6]}, {"text": "Amounts recognized on derivative represent the effective portion of the fixed price diesel swaps.", "bbox": [194.9, 877.7, 1003.5, 898.6]}, {"text": "(3)", "bbox": [153.2, 902.7, 177.5, 923.6]}, {"text": "Amounts recognized on hedged item reflect the use of 9.7 million, 6.3 million and 5.9 million gallons of", "bbox": [194.9, 902.7, 1103.7, 923.6]}, {"text": "diesel covered by the fixed price swaps during the years ended December 31, 2013, 2012 and 2011,", "bbox": [194.9, 927.8, 1103.8, 948.6]}, {"text": "respectively.", "bbox": [194.9, 952.8, 300.8, 973.6]}, {"text": "11.", "bbox": [153.2, 1006.6, 179.3, 1027.5]}, {"text": "Fair Value Measurements", "bbox": [200.1, 1006.6, 431.7, 1027.5]}, {"text": "We account for certain assets and liabilities at fair value, and categorize each of our fair value measurements", "bbox": [194.9, 1041.6, 1103.5, 1062.4]}, {"text": "in one of the following three levels based on the lowest level input that is significant to the fair value", "bbox": [153.2, 1066.6, 1103.7, 1087.4]}, {"text": "measurement in its entirety:", "bbox": [153.2, 1091.6, 385.8, 1112.4]}, {"text": "Level 1—Inputs to the valuation methodology are unadjusted quoted prices in active markets for identical", "bbox": [194.9, 1126.3, 1103.6, 1147.1]}, {"text": "assets or liabilities.", "bbox": [153.2, 1151.3, 312.6, 1172.1]}, {"text": "Level 2—Observable inputs other than quoted prices in active markets for identical assets and liabilities", "bbox": [194.9, 1186.0, 1103.4, 1206.8]}, {"text": "include:", "bbox": [153.2, 1211.0, 220.4, 1231.9]}, {"text": "a) quoted prices for similar assets or liabilities in active markets;", "bbox": [194.9, 1236.0, 734.7, 1256.9]}, {"text": "b) quoted prices for identical or similar assets or liabilities in inactive markets;", "bbox": [194.9, 1270.7, 851.9, 1291.6]}, {"text": "c) inputs other than quoted prices that are observable for the asset or liability;", "bbox": [194.9, 1305.4, 841.6, 1326.3]}, {"text": "d) inputs that are derived principally from or corroborated by observable market data by correlation or other", "bbox": [194.9, 1340.1, 1103.7, 1361.0]}, {"text": "means.", "bbox": [153.2, 1365.1, 211.7, 1386.0]}, {"text": "If the asset or liability has a specified (contractual) term, the Level 2 input must be observable for", "bbox": [194.9, 1399.8, 1103.7, 1420.7]}, {"text": "substantially the full term of the asset or liability.", "bbox": [153.2, 1424.9, 564.6, 1445.7]}, {"text": "77", "bbox": [618.1, 1475.4, 638.9, 1496.2]}]}